#Common commands

#To get information about pods:
```
kubectl get pods 
```
```
kubectl describe pod POD_NAME
```

# To get cluster info
```
kubectl cluster-info
```
# To get information about nodes:
```
kubectl get nodes
```

# To create a file 
```
kubectl create -f app.yml 
```

# To get services:
```
kubectl get svc  
```

# To get the information about horizontal pod autoscaler
```
kubectl get hpa
```
```
kubectl describe hpa hpa_name
```
